## Tableaux Proving

```elixir
import ShotDs.Hol.Sigils
import ShotTx.Prover
```

```elixir
~f"?[X: $o]: X" |> prove
```

```elixir
~f"a & b => a" |> prove
```

```elixir
~f"a => (a | b)" |> prove
```

```elixir
~f"~?[F : $i>$i>$o]: ![Y: $i>$o]: ?[X: $i]: F @ X = Y" |> prove
```

```elixir
~f"p @ (a & b) => p @ (b & a)" |> prove
```

```elixir
~f"![X : $o, Y : $o]: p @ X & p @ Y => p @ (X & Y)" |> prove
```

```elixir
~f"""
(
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: ~X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $false) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $true)
)
=>
![Y : $o>$o]: p @ Y
"""
|> prove
```

```elixir
~f"""
(
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: ~X) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $false) &
  (p @ ^[X : $o]: $true)
)
=>
?[Y : $o>$o]: ~ p @ Y
"""
|> prove
```

```elixir
~f"p @ a & p @ b => p @ (a & b)" |> prove
```

```elixir
~f"p @ a & q @ a => ?[X : $i>$o]: X @ a & X @ b" |> prove
```

